I totally agree that I do not like other melees hitting the mob too soon.  I see this mostly with like level 52-54 peeps in their first PoP group.  When I see it I send them a polite tell to get things ironed out and 99.999% of the time things work better fast.  <br>
<br>
You can prolly lump this into a general &quot;people who don't know how to control their own aggro&quot; category.  <br>
<br>
I was grouped with a Wizzie who just dinged 60 and was waiting to mem a new DD spell he couldn't wait to use.  Of course he nuked too soon and got aggro.  Within a kill or two he was back to &quot;stand-nuke-sit&quot; at the right time.  He learned the right time to use that nuke and made the proper adjustments.  Props to Zifnabb the wizzie for that.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=1909.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=1909.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=1909.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=1909.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=1909.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showMessageRange?topicID=1909.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a> <b>7</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showPrevMessage?topicID=1909.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showNextMessage?topicID=1909.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1909.topic&index=133><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.emailToFriend?topicID=1909.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a